	<br>
	<div style="text-align:right;">
		KOTAKA, Veridiana Maffessoni<sup>1</sup>; KOZICKI, Katya<sup>2</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa CNPq-PIBIC		<BR>
